  [ Apollon Oikonomopoulos ]
  * New upstream development version

  [ Vincent Bernat ]
  * Add support for systemd. Currently, /etc/default/haproxy is not used
    when using systemd.

 -- Vincent Bernat <bernat@debian.org>  Sun, 26 May 2013 12:33:00 +0200

